Everything working fine, and then hit ^space part way through a class name, got
an error dialog "The command for the key you pressed failed", and a stack dump
in the error log.

Restarting didn't fix the problem. It only happens in one source file it seems,
had been working fine earlier. I tried anywhere in the source, didn't make a
difference. Works as expected in other sources. Restarting with -clean also
doesn't help.
